#: ../../L/like-kicking-dead-whales-down-the-beach.rst:9
msgid ""
"Describes a slow, difficult, and disgusting process. First popularized by a "
"famous quote about the difficulty of getting work done under one of IBM's "
"mainframe OSes. \"Well, you could write a C compiler in COBOL, but it would "
"be like kicking dead whales down the beach.\" See also :ref:`fear-and-"
"loathing`\\."
msgstr ""
"遅く、困難で、不快な過程を表す。IBMのメインフレームOSの一つの下で作業を成し遂げることの難しさについての有名な言葉によって最初に広まった。「まあ、COBOLでCコンパイラを書くこともできるが、それは死んだクジラを浜辺で蹴り進めるようなものだろう。」\\"
" :ref:`fear-and-loathing`\\ も参照。"
